所謂'''人造胚晶'''<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://terms.naer.edu.tw/detail/657923/?index=5 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2017-02-17 |archive-date=2017-02-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170226131420/http://terms.naer.edu.tw/detail/657923/?index=5 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，係指透過合成手段製出之[[單晶|單晶]]{{tsl|en|ingot|晶錠}}。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=WJzmBQAAQBAJ&pg=PA56&lpg=PA56&dq=boule+silicon&source=bl&ots=Sv_meo8_ld&sig=7XCp7sw4ElO-tpoTm5eDGpfv7hY&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwiLuNPG9abSAhUELcAKHUhnCB04ChDoAQhIMAk#v=onepage&q=boule%20silicon&f=false|title=fundementals of silicon carbide technology|accessdate=2017-02-25|archive-date=2019-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190929165036/https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=WJzmBQAAQBAJ&pg=PA56&lpg=PA56&dq=boule+silicon&source=bl&ots=Sv_meo8_ld&sig=7XCp7sw4ElO-tpoTm5eDGpfv7hY&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwiLuNPG9abSAhUELcAKHUhnCB04ChDoAQhIMAk#v=onepage&q=boule%20silicon&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[矽|矽]]之人造胚晶乃當今多數[[積體電路|積體電路]]所用之基礎原料。

[[Image:Monokristalines_Silizium_für_die_Waferherstellung.jpg|thumb]]

今之[[半導體|半導體]]產業有數種方法可以製造人造胚晶, 如[[布里奇曼-史托巴格法|布里奇曼法]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=izaSIlOahJkC&pg=PA485&dq=bridgman+technique&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwjPzIyS96bSAhUmC8AKHdgaC2MQ6AEIPjAF#v=onepage&q=bridgman%20technique&f=false|title=crystal growth handbook|deadurl=no|accessdate=February 25, 2017|archive-date=2019-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190930202502/https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=izaSIlOahJkC&pg=PA485&dq=bridgman+technique&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwjPzIyS96bSAhUmC8AKHdgaC2MQ6AEIPjAF#v=onepage&q=bridgman%20technique&f=false}}</ref>、[[柴可拉斯基法|柴式拉晶法]]等，產物往往以圓柱體之晶棒型式居多。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=ce-__G-L5iEC&pg=PP11&dq=Czochralski+process&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwjL17bo9qbSAhWKCsAKHRwPA1IQ6AEIKTAE#v=onepage&q=Czochralski%20process&f=false|title=continuous czochralski process development|accessdate=2017-02-25|archive-date=2019-10-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191013165651/https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=ce-__G-L5iEC&pg=PP11&dq=Czochralski+process&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwjL17bo9qbSAhWKCsAKHRwPA1IQ6AEIKTAE#v=onepage&q=Czochralski%20process&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>

若以柴式拉晶法拉造人造胚晶，須先備妥一[[晶種|晶種]]，始得進行後續造大晶體、晶錠之程序。晶種沾入純矽熔融液，然後再緩緩將之拉起。凝固自熔融液的新晶體將有與晶種相同之秩序，進而形成圓柱型的大顆單晶，是為人造胚晶。

圓柱型之人造胚晶通常會被鑽石鋸刀切成[[晶圓|晶圓片]]。晶圓片又經[[拋光|拋光]]有了平整的表面，才能成為適合製造[[半導體裝置|半導體裝置]]的基板。同樣的製程也可以用來製造[[藍寶石|藍寶石]]基板。藍寶石基板是製造藍色、白色[[發光二極體|發光二極體]]的材料，也可用在特殊用途的{{link-en|光窗|Optical window#Technology}}<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://terms.naer.edu.tw/detail/262001/?index=1 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2017-02-17 |archive-date=2019-07-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190718120721/http://terms.naer.edu.tw/detail/262001/?index=1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>或手錶的保護殼。

